** Hitting a target with 0 stack with evolved ''Void Seeker'': {{tt|{{as|12 − 48 (based on level)|magic damage}}|3 stacks, 4 - 16 each}} {{tt|{{as|(+ 3 − 24 (based on level)|buzzword}}|0 stack + 1 stack + 2 stacks, 1 - 8 each}} {{tt|{{as|(+ {{fd|52.5}}% AP)}}|0 stack AP ratio 15% + 1 stack AP ratio 17.5% + 2 stacks AP ratio 20%}}
** Hitting a target with 2 stacks with evolved ''Void Seeker'': {{tt|{{as|12 − 48 (based on level)|magic damage}}|3 stacks, 4 - 16 each}} {{tt|{{as|(+ 9 − 72 (based on level)|buzzword}}|2 stacks + 3 stacks + 4 stacks, 1 - 8 each}} {{tt|{{as|(+ {{fd|67.5}}% AP)}}|2 stacks AP ratio 20% + 3 stacks AP ratio 22.5% + 4 stacks AP ratio 25%}}
